sunshine….<\/p>","content_model":"Obsidian","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/obsidian","link_text":"Shop The Product"}},"item_TpMeDj":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/281025_8093806952694_2cc9341d_0f57_4e88_ace2_b1bee85fa3cf.webp","title":"Robin O.","content_title":"WOW!","desc":"<p>I have been researching electric bikes for over two years trying to find the perfect one for me. I think that the Obsidian is the one. It checks all the boxes for me with payload, range, geometry, and hopefully price.<\/p>","content_model":"Obsidian","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/obsidian","link_text":"Shop The Product"}},"item_tz99H6":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/281025_7734531064054_63a49e5d_d4b1_440b_9cae_a79ec7a47c9d.webp","title":"Errol","content_title":"Very happy with my purchase.","desc":"<p>I bought the Basalt together with another manufacturers bike in the same price range. The Basalt has a much sturdier build, was easier to assemble, and looks better! Very happy with my purchase.<\/p>","content_model":"Basalt","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/basalt","link_text":"Shop The Product"}},"item_EQBxUf":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/281025_7734556786934_8f27d303_1327_4690_a180_54045be6f88d.webp","title":"Jacob","content_title":"I really love this Basalt electric bike! ! ","desc":"<p>The bike looks exactly as I expected it to, and secondly, it arrived quickly and I didn't have to wait long. I installed it quickly according to the instructions and started using it. I'm really happy with this bike, it completely exceeded my expectations.<\/p>","content_model":"Basalt ST","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/basalt-st","link_text":"Shop The Product"}},"item_GJhz48":{"type":"item","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/281025_7444055884022_03e95afa_8fd6_419a_8112_14f9b17948d8.webp","title":"Natalie","content_title":"Luv this bike","desc":"<p>My first E-bike (Mesa Plus ST) and I luv luv luv it! Everything about this purchase has been superior. Thank you Mokwheel for making this purchase an easy choice and fun. Just a few words to describe my bike: Solid, performance, exhilarating, comfort, addicting, worth the money. Just do it--no regrets here.<\/p>","content_model":"Mesa Plus ST","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/mesa-plus-st","link_text":"Shop The Product"}},"item_cg6PPq":{"type":"item","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Rectangle_780_31f22f64-a115-4542-80db-00c87e5fee08.jpg","title":"Rob S.","content_title":"Mesa Plus ST","desc":"<p>Best bike I ever owned ! I have had the bike since September I already have over 1000 miles on it I think I ride it more than my Harley road king Highly recommended strong fast durable bike<\/p>","content_model":"Mesa Plus ST","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/mesa-plus-st","link_text":"Shop The Product"}},"item_YxB3UX":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/281025_8373225324790_5a4320c5_4ab3_4ec7_b9ec_4669459e9b38.webp","title":"Ellie","content_title":"Simple to use","desc":"<p>This bike is clean and practical. It's a pleasure to ride, very smooth, value for money, don't miss it, don't waste your money on other e-bike shopping platforms or other e-bike brands, buy a mokwheel!<\/p>","content_model":"Slate","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/slate","link_text":"Shop The Product"}}},"block_order":["item_8zXBtJ","item_4tjQgC","item_TpMeDj","item_tz99H6","item_EQBxUf","item_GJhz48","item_cg6PPq","item_YxB3UX"],"custom_css":["@media (max-width: 999px) {.alp-index-remark-wrapper {padding-bottom: 60px; }}"],"settings":{"title":"Customer Favorites","link_text_title":"View More","link_url_title":"shopify:\/\/pages\/electric-bike-reviews","heading_type":"h2","image_aspect_ratio":"1\/1","block_max_width":"420px","bg_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#000000","container":"alp-container-fluid","padding_top":30,"padding_bottom":30,"reset_spacing":true}},"138b3cf9-d014-4399-8616-e82efe61cea5":{"type":"jd-product-facet","blocks":{"eda7d8d3-a5ef-49e7-9c62-cbd61346dc15":{"type":"item","settings":{"product_list":["solar-panel-inverter","230wsolar-panel-inverter","lnverter-2","bundle-accessories-kits-3","bundle-accessories-kits-4","battery-basalt-basalt-st","battery-tor-plus","front-mounted-basket-1","helmet","pet-shed-flat-roof-1","rear-rack-obsidian","water-bottle-holder-2"]}}},"block_order":["eda7d8d3-a5ef-49e7-9c62-cbd61346dc15"],"custom_css":[],"settings":{"title":"Accessories Related To Ebikes","link_text":"view all accessories","link_url":"https:\/\/www.mokwheel.com\/collections\/accessory","bg_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#000000","container":"alp-container-fluid","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":30,"reset_spacing":true}},"832923b2-692e-4f30-a244-27c2b16b108b":{"type":"jd-help-faq","blocks":{"4fa3f05e-b704-412a-be3e-3027c3030623":{"type":"item_tab","settings":{"faqs_question":"What should I look for when buying an ebike for sale?","faqs_answer":"<p>When buying an ebike, consider motor power (e.g., 500W–1300W), battery range (miles per charge), terrain compatibility (city, mountain, off-road), frame style (step-through vs. high-step), and additional features like suspension, racks, or solar charging. Mokwheel offers a wide range of ebikes for every riding need.<br\/><\/p>"}},"2370438d-635e-494d-8677-da7e51630077":{"type":"item_tab","settings":{"faqs_question":"Are there any seasonal ebike for sale deals?","faqs_answer":"<p>Yes! Many brands, including Mokwheel, offer seasonal promotions like summer or holiday sales. These often include significant discounts (up to $800 off), bundle deals, and free accessories. Check the <a href=\"\/pages\/promotion-landing\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Promotion Landing\"><strong>Promotion<\/strong><\/a> page for the latest offers.<\/p>"}},"a2a01fbb-5b86-4862-98b4-f091a0fb5c4d":{"type":"item_tab","settings":{"faqs_question":"Do they require special maintenance?","faqs_answer":"<p>Compared to regular electric bikes, off-road e-bikes require periodic maintenance, including checking the suspension system, lubricating the chain, monitoring tire pressure, and inspecting brake wear to ensure optimal performance and safety.<\/p>"}},"item_tab_xjhLKT":{"type":"item_tab","settings":{"faqs_question":"Do ebikes for sale come with a warranty?","faqs_answer":"<p>Most reputable ebike brands offer a warranty—typically 1–2 years covering the motor, battery, and frame. Mokwheel provides <strong>2 years limited warranty<\/strong> and a <strong>15-day risk-free trial<\/strong>, ensuring you shop with confidence.<br\/><\/p>"}},"item_tab_YHpVXM":{"type":"item_tab","settings":{"faqs_question":"Can I test ride or return an ebike I bought on sale?","faqs_answer":"<p>Some brands and dealers offer <a href=\"\/pages\/ebike-test-ride-apply\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Book a Test Ride\"><strong>test rides or flexible return policies<\/strong><\/a>. Mokwheel, for example, offers a <strong>15-day trial period<\/strong> even for ebikes purchased during sale events, giving you peace of mind to ride before you fully commit.<\/p>"}},"item_tab_9FNcYj":{"type":"item_tab","settings":{"faqs_question":"Are financing options available for ebike for sale promotions?","faqs_answer":"<p>Yes, many online stores—including Mokwheel—provide <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mokwheel.com\/pages\/financing-program\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"0% interest installment plans\"><strong>0% interest installment plans<\/strong><\/a> during sales, making it easier to own an ebike without upfront full payment.<\/p>"}},"item_tab_d6NPDL":{"type":"item_tab","settings":{"faqs_question":"Are ebikes for sale suitable for hills and rough terrain?","faqs_answer":"<p>Absolutely. Look for high-torque motors (like Mokwheel’s 1100W–1300W models), wide fat tires, and full suspension systems for enhanced control and comfort on hills or off-road paths. Many ebikes on sale are built for both city and rugged trails.<\/p>"}},"item_tab_wajaV8":{"type":"item_tab","settings":{"faqs_question":"How do I find an Mokwheel e-bike store near me?","faqs_answer":"<p>If you're looking for Mokwheel e-bike stores,<a href=\"\/pages\/our-dealers\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Find a Dealer\"><strong> please visit one of our authorized dealers<\/strong><\/a>. They offer a full range of models, provide test rides, and will walk you through the features and performance of each e-bike.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["4fa3f05e-b704-412a-be3e-3027c3030623","2370438d-635e-494d-8677-da7e51630077","a2a01fbb-5b86-4862-98b4-f091a0fb5c4d","item_tab_xjhLKT","item_tab_YHpVXM","item_tab_9FNcYj","item_tab_d6NPDL","item_tab_wajaV8"],"settings":{"faqtitle":"E-Bikes For Sale FAQs","bg_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#000000","container":"alp-container-fluid","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false,"show_all":false}}},"order":["banner","5b85dcc6-5d97-4a27-be40-bcfb14a25ddb","068efb60-06f6-49bb-a670-94ece84744ea","product-grid","alp_main_products_list_mPLKa9","312dd263-140c-4f0b-8224-e3bdfc634934","55941165-a236-4f8e-b9e2-3385a441c801","alp_index_remark_c_dTMwwn","138b3cf9-d014-4399-8616-e82efe61cea5","832923b2-692e-4f30-a244-27c2b16b108b"]}